data.description: Discover the charm of this residence in the highly desirable Lomas Del Este neighborhood on a corner lot. This stunning home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by bright, spacious living areas, with a well-appointed kitchen  with an island that invites you to enjoy and entertain. The master suite provides a serene retreat with its own full bath, double vanities and ample closet space. Outside, the backyard is just waiting on you to turn it into your own private oasis. Located in a desirable area, this residence provides easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment and Fort Bliss. Come and discover the perfect home!
